Office Profile

   The Cleveland Division of the FBI employs 173 Special Agents and over
   134 professional support employees. The office is headquartered in
   downtown Cleveland with nine resident agencies located in the
   surrounding cities.

Cleveland Headquarters

   (Covers Cuyahoga County)


    1240 East Ninth St., Suite 3005, Cleveland, Ohio 44199


    (216) 522-1400

